Employment status.label: Employment status
Employment status.description: The youth unemployment rate is the percentage of youth in the labour force that are unemployed

Unemployment - Official.label: Unemployment - Official
Unemployment - Official.description: According to the official definition, a person is unemployed if he or she is (a) without work, (b) available to work, and (c) actively seeking work.

Unemployment - Expanded.label: Unemployment - Expanded
Unemployment - Expanded.description: According to the expanded definition, a person is unemployed if he or she is (a) without work, and (b) available to work

Not in Employment, Education and Trainin.label: Not in Employment, Education and Training (NEET) status
